cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DS 

The paper discusses the evaluation of Artificial Intelligence tasks, specifically Text Clustering, which falls under Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) sub-categories. The paper also introduces a new metric, which can be applied to a variety of AI tasks, indicating its relevance to Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Finally, the paper discusses the sensitivity of the results to the weighting scheme used to combine the metrics, which is a common issue in Data Science (cs.DS) sub-category.
